  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "synopsis",
      "abstract": "This Act creates a rebuttable presumption that the Court shall order equal parenting time if the parties live within 25 miles of the child\u2019s daycare or school. Equal parenting time may be amended if it is determined a parent is not tending to the child\u2019s health or educational needs."
    }
